    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractModelDescriptionConnector, AbstractModelDescriptionInboundPort, AbstractModelDescriptionOutboundPort, EventsExchangingConnector, EventsExchangingInboundPort, EventsExchangingOutboundPort, ParentNotificationConnector, ParentNotificationInboundPort, ParentNotificationOutboundPort, SimulatorConnector, SimulatorInboundPort, SimulatorOutboundPort

    public interface ModelDescriptionCI
extends fr.sorbonne_u.components.interfaces.OfferedCI, fr.sorbonne_u.components.interfaces.RequiredCI, fr.sorbonne_u.devs_simulation.interfaces.ModelDescriptionI
    The component interface ModelDescriptionCI declares the methods that can be used to get information from simulation models directly or through their simulation engine or any other proxy reference.

    Description

    Invariant

     invariant      true
